| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5156 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 59d38996-8f77-5c5d-b3f1-22a5e092f9f6"
